Program: Letter from America by Alistair Cooke
Title: Mayor Koch snowed under
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b040brqn
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 29 Jan 1978
New York's Mayor Koch under attack after snow storms hit the city. This archive edition of Letter from America was recorded by one of two listeners, who between them taped and labelled over 650 Letter From America programmes from 1973 to 1989. It was restored by the BBC in 2014.